data.description: Spacious 4-Bedroom 2.5 Bath Home in Highly Sought-After Area on Greenbelt.  The Home is in top-rated schools, including Johnson High School.  The Home features a Living and Dining area and a vast Family Room with natural light streaming in from windows and patio door while you enjoy an evening by the wood-burning Fireplace.  The Kitchen features Granite Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, White Cabinets, and an open floor plan that looks into the Family room and Breakfast area.  The Primary Bedroom is HUGE with a walk-in closet, providing ample space for all your belongings.  When it's time to relax, enjoy a movie in the Gameroom with wall space wide enough for an 85" TV.  Walk out to the backyard and enjoy the Privacy on a 20' X 15' Patio that looks onto a Greenbelt!  The community offers a Basketball Court, Playground area, and walking trail.  The Home's location is also convenient, as it's just minutes away from North Central Baptist, Methodist Hospital Stone Oak, BluePearl Pet Hospital, Costco, restaurant, TPC shopping, entertainment, and easy highway access onto Hwy 281/1604.  This Home is an excellent opportunity to own an incredible home in a fantastic area.
